name: Emily
bio: aka Moo-Moo, aka Moo-Moo Magoo. 5 years old. Loves fluffy pillows and snuggles. Adopted from Hudson's Halfway Home, which rescues dogs with special needs. (She has a cleft palate.)

name: Geno
bio: aka Gee-Gee, aka Gee-Gee McGee. 4 years old. Loves eating out of the garbage, turning fetch into tug of war, napping by the vent. Adopted from Hudson's Halfway Home. which rescues dogs with special needs. (He has a cleft palate.)

name: Clover
bio: Clover (aka Duke Clovington, aka Professor Good Boy) loves cuddling, going on adventures, and eating cheese. When he's not out camping or hiking he likes to lounge in the sun, nap in bed, and chew any underwear that was accidentally left on the ground.
